# Main Client Flows
- Online (WAN): (Registration) -> Login                        -> Battle List -> Create Battle -> Battle Room -> Parametrize? -> Play
- Local (LAN):                 -> Pick Name -> [Spawns Server] -> Battle List -> Create Battle -> Battle Room -> Parametrize? -> Play
- Offline:                     -> Pick Name                    ->             -> Create Battle -> Battle Room -> Parametrize? -> Play

# Side Flows
- Spring Config
- Launcher Config
- Downloads View

